<h2>Vuer: An Event-Driven, Declarative Visualization Toolkit for GenAI and Robotics
<br/>
<img src="https://api.netlify.com/api/v1/badges/2df7f3ba-1a26-4047-b76a-d7401f907bb5/deploy-status" alt="Production">
